enhanced_by.reason: The hashrateResaleRequest method must be executed before hashrateResaleDetail to ensure that the configId and userName are set up correctly.
The hashrateResaleList method can provide necessary context about the resale configurations, which can be useful before fetching detailed information.
Both hashrateResaleDetail and bonusList methods return detailed lists related to mining activities, which can inform the construction of assertions for hashrateResaleDetail.
The earningList method returns earnings details, which can be similar in structure to the details returned by hashrateResaleDetail, aiding in assertion construction.
